  <exercise>
    <statement>
      <p>
        Let <m>C[0,10]</m> be the vector space of continuous functions defined <m>[0,10] \to \rr</m>, and let <m>D[0,10]</m> be the set of differentiable functions defined <m>[0,10] \to \rr</m>.
      </p>
      <p>
        For each of the following, determine whether or not the subset <m>W</m> of <m>C[0,10]</m> is a subspace of <m>C[0,10]</m>. Explain your answers.
