              <m>W = \{ f \in D[0,10] \mid f'(1)=0 \}</m>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              <m>W = \{ f \in D[0,10] \mid f'(1)=1 \}</m>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
